BotStrategyOut.description:
Unified response containing both bot and strategy details.

Returned by POST /bot-strategy/create and PATCH /bot-strategy/{bot_id}.

Example response::

    {
        "bot": {
            "id": 5,
            "bot_name": "my_bot",
            "status": "stopped",
            "strategy_name": "MyRSIStrategy",
            ...
        },
        "strategy": {
            "id": 12,
            "bot_id": 5,
            "name": "MyRSIStrategy",
            "strategy_type": "statistical",
            "configurations": { ... },
            ...
        }
    }
